Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遼闊的天空\N無數的星星閃閃發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.38,0:00:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映出濕潤的眼眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.48,0:00:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常常走的這條路\N街道景緻不變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.13,0:00:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無趣的日子 好想擺脫這一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.90,0:00:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又藍又高的天空\N遼闊的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同這世上所有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深信自己可以得到\N都可以掌控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.25,0:01:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N朝幼時所描繪的夢想前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.95,0:01:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊握的手\N能感受到你傳來的溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.96,0:01:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後所抵達的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.06,0:01:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定也是\N沒有人知道的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.40,0:01:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就衝向 未知的明日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是第三護衛艦亞瑪特拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成宇宙飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告各部門目前情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告各部門目前情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航宙管制 一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.85,0:02:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關部 一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊管制 一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.02,0:02:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊管制 一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.49,0:02:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關部 航宙管制\N一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.69,0:02:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N目前宇宙航行一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再機小時\N就可以抵達行星奇比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來亞瑪特拉斯的航行試驗\N將可以順利結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們防衛大學宇宙戰科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.44,0:03:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第73期的\N宇宙航行實習也將結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.35,0:03:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香月候補生的聲音甜美\N聽起來很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.29,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像秀過\N數位影音傳出來的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是第73期的學生主席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前的成績都很平均
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 成績不夠優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.80,0:03:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙戰鬥的模擬戰和\N戰史研究的成績好像都很優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我擅長玩遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.94,0:03:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有\N我對自己的記憶力很有信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果參加銀河網的猜謎節目\N說不定還能贏得優勝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.56,0:03:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薪水\N可能會比當自衛官高出十倍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.73,0:03:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香月候補生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.43,0:04:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很有成為最佳艦長的潛力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問還有一點什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.07,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個祕書妳是最糟糕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有種被人玩弄的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一話\N(倒數計時)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得聽起來\N沒有什麼惡意呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他是惡意的\N我一定會當場哭給他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.28,0:04:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓他失望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳即使用演的\N也絕對會讓對方滿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是妳最拿手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的處世方式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的不加入自衛隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢業之後\N妳就真的要跟大家分開了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳不同 沒有任何的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不討厭玩遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我討厭真正的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想進入一流企業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找一個好男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 珊麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳心情好像很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳們說\N我跟他說話了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 妳跟泰凱說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 射擊管制 一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.98,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只說這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就很滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欣諾\N我看妳應該去談戀愛才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和大家的出路又不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談了也是白談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.66,0:05:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想出路跟談戀愛\N沒有絕對關係喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 研習時期的聯誼費用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.10,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我算過囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人是20110圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.14,0:05:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 費用\N連女同學都要繳費啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 妳是什麼時代的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生請女生的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那已經是\N機個世紀前的陳年老事了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 這是我的妳拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.79,0:06:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照傳統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦的醫療班本來就愛喝酒嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接跟他說不就得了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我跟雷娜是網友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 我也付清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家做好\N下宇宙船的準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 間宮同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.62,0:06:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天行星奇比\N標準時間上午6點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翰林亞達星域行星國家同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於行星國家奇比正式宣戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.69,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國戰艦猛烈攻擊\N奇比的護衛艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓奇比的護衛艦\N遭受到毀滅性的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 正式宣戰\N針對這場戰役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.57,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入翰林亞達星域\N戰爭已經開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰阪同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰阪同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快去看看\N到底發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.68,0:07:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家先坐下來\N先回到自己的座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.12,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別激動 上面叫我們男生\N都來這裡待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於士官候補生\N則在食堂待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.73,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 原來這裡\N是女人的天地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰凱 到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道啊\N妳問我也沒有用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說王國突然對奇比宣戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且突然襲擊\N第二護衛艦邁茲爾艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個新聞剛剛已經報過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了這個之外\N還知道些什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜政府一定會馬上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當今的政府\N的確有可能會這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.05,0:07:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前總理的姪女所說的話\N感覺上特別有說服力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為推翻我伯父政權的\N這些政府首腦們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本上就是很討厭麻煩的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有人稱此為和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上投降這件事\N看起來可能是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新特 你聽說些什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面叫我們去食堂待命後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現役士官們\N開始準備起小型艦艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來這艘戰艦\N不會回到奇比行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而會衛星軌道上先解除武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為引擎的馬力\N比剛剛低多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘戰艦\N在還沒抵達奇比之前就會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.99,0:08:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光聽引擎的聲音\N就能夠知道戰艦的動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是老爹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.76,0:08:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我老爹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.53,0:08:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇比\N在完全不反擊的情況下投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們 接下來會怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們也只能\N緊隨奇比的自衛官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘小艦艇\N離開這艘戰艦回奇比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在\N王國的戰鬥機護送下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.41,0:08:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自衛隊會解散\N原本想加入自衛隊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得趕快開始\N四處應徵工作才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子\N我也應該去唸普通大學好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.46,0:09:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到國家投降雖然都很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果真的打起仗來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我們\N就非得上戰場不可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這裡面\N就會出現犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話\N還真是瞧不起我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫現役自衛官\N先行離開戰艦的這種作法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.31,0:09:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為擔心自衛官\N會劫持這艘戰艦造反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們\N真的這麼沒有威脅性嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.98,0:09:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我們還只是大學生\N這也是沒有辦法的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(解除武裝)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.39,0:09:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對\N有些事只有我們才辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟那些教官們不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有養家這種後顧之憂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.87,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.87,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以劫持這艘戰艦\N跟王國來個對決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼可能這麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.84,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算我們沒有家要養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是別忘了\N還有家人在等我們回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說的沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在沒有\N補給支援的情況之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想跟王國對決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在於有沒有支援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能夠報邁茲爾\N被毀滅的仇這樣就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是要持續奮戰\N直到物資用盡為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們 是不是瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.31,0:10:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想過\N光靠這一艘戰艦可以打敗王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於為了私利\N不斷侵略他國的王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的無法原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠理解妳的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在場的每一個人\N心情應該都會跟妳一樣才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王國會要求\N自動放棄軍事力量的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取消所有軍備採購買賣契約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再由王國出面\N以便宜的價格收購
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來擴充王國的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.57,0:10:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.87,0:10:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說\N這艘戰艦會暫時成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製造廠商的\N星間企業AGI的資產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.51,0:10:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.68,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都有權利收購那艘戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 那真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.32,0:11:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神崎同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意付錢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要收購
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.22,0:11:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙戰艦一艘造價多少錢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.76,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出門在外\N身上沒這麼多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我倒是可以\N找到金主出錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.27,0:11:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們可以找\N和王國敵對的行星國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出面來協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支援我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們肯為了幫我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而有和王國交戰的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有國家肯這麼做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說是同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟不像一塊岩石那麼堅固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的交涉成功的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,間宮同學願意與王國對決嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能夠合法取得這艘戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且真的有人肯支援的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們或許真的可以打打看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無稽之談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種像在變魔法的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不可能實現嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用變魔法來比喻不太恰當啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香月同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:12:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我現在就去通信室\N跟出資的金主們交涉看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.31,0:12:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你打算跟誰交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是能夠先告訴我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟銀河網路事業交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.63,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被翰林耶達星域行星\N國家同盟正式宣戰後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行星國家奇比馬上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且正式發表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入國家同盟聲明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.34,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是奇比自衛隊的\N士官候補同學們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聽從命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.98,0:12:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將航行實習使用的\N第三護衛艦亞瑪特拉斯戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.08,0:12:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從亞里瑪傑內拉爾\N音達斯得亞魯手中收購
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.68,0:12:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等新聞一報完\N就要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.06,0:12:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離正式播出還有5分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是銀河網宇宙飛船電台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是記者狄達米爾克夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我目前所在的位置是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.28,0:13:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由護衛艦\N亞瑪特拉斯的機關部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑪特拉斯原本是屬於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行星國家奇比的資產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今被士官候補生們所收購
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替代政府和王國展開對決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要的事就不要說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是期盼已久的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙戰爭實況轉播耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鏡頭前的我漂亮嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關部拍到這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改去艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.47,0:13:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.17,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要記得叫我製作人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N我會再來採訪你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼很粗心大意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.11,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一級的戰鬥準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要做好隨時都能\N發動最大戰速的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.89,0:14:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從空間極座標\N轉換成3次元經緯座標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索偵查敵人系統無感應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 距離轉播還有1分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欣諾 妳的妝化得很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.75,0:14:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.78,0:14:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過最重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上不上鏡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.03,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離百萬二千機何距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位從佳瑪變成BETA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.35,0:14:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在收看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙飛行船新聞的觀眾們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.92,0:15:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這艘敵艦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由護衛艦亞瑪特拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.33,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久即將與這艘敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展開一場激烈的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這種情況看起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要怎麼採取迴避行動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成敵人不打算迴避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.11,0:15:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有時間跟妳開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非所有的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.48,0:15:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是用相同的\N設計理念打造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.89,0:15:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦發出了閃光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和敵艦的距離是97萬5000
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相對速度是5萬7000
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.76,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙方等速運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離97萬公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然從那麼遠的地方發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是距離遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.94,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的射程是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦最大射程的二倍以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦開始攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.54,0:15:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算我們攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也打不到對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.88,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以目前的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像那樣反擊敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要在3小時以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這段期間內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能乖乖被打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能從光源的種類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來判斷敵艦的武器呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光源的種類好像是等離子液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如波動狀的放射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周期是20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能是軌道槍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小鋼珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告 射擊管制區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桐生副艦長來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鋼珠很難對付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是單純地\N用實體彈向我艦射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但絕不能輕忽它的破壞力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然命中率不太高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像面對\N一個槍法不好亂射的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.14,0:16:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航行管制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三上副艦長來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成冰阪候補生的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.38,0:16:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是軌道槍沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.82,0:16:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據判斷應該是軌道槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.06,0:16:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家繼續採取迴避行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且朝主砲射程範圍接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們來真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.53,0:16:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本打不到敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會把我艦的砲彈耗盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是從這麼遠的距離發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們不會覺得很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼武器\N只要距離過遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中率就一定會降低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此根本沒有必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白白浪費這些砲彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是敵艦卻採取主動攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.48,0:17:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.18,0:17:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認定有異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是過度擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關大家的生死問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有所謂的過度擔心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.49,0:17:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳太過於謹慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會錯失攻擊機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不清楚敵艦意圖的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯莽接近是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦的意圖很清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是負責亞瑪特拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人工智能伊索的技術士官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.87,0:17:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結城席明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欣諾說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦完全沒有閃避之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦想等我們進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射程範圍內時\N再跟我艦一決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雖然說艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.48,0:17:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是士官候補生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N只有這傢伙是自衛官的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人工智能的維修工程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,候補生果然還是做不來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說\N那傢伙就是公然違反軍紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在敵艦沒有把小行星吃光之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該會持續攻擊我艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃光小行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為敵艦是小行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是金屬的結合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有搭載著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將金屬變成彈丸的裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說它是一艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像工廠般的宇宙砲台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然一邊迴避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再以最快的速度前往攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採取這種作戰策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功率是27%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.42,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去並沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受過這種戰鬥訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.23,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就是違背常理嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.23,0:18:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然會有這種自製彈丸的砲台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有沒有\N任何遮蔽的物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡附近倒是有機個小行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以敵艦才會\N選這裡作為戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是\N擁有豐富戰爭經驗的王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欣諾 妳有什麼辦法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把護衛艦\N移到小行星的陰影處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度採用第2戰速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方向改為1點鐘的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進到小行星的陰影處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.79,0:18:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第2戰速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方向改為1點鐘的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.59,0:18:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進小行星陰影處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解 第2戰速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解 方向為1點鐘的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,座標 2660 BETA 2110
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝小行星飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個菜鳥到底想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就把節目搞砸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放過妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿小行星當盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移動到敵艦的有效射程範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.52,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前針對以長距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊方式攻打過來的敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞馬特拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.56,0:19:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正準備以小行星\N作為盾牌勇敢迎戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大戰速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀河網的節目王國\N應該也收看得到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.17,0:19:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說\N他們對於我們的戰略瞭若指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒有關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.81,0:19:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒有辦法的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.68,0:19:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫我們\N已經把播放權賣給銀河網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就是自殺嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離射程範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再120秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入射程範圍內之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再脫離小行星的陰影處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有正確觀測敵艦的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是無法命中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要給泰凱1分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.77,0:20:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對能瞄準敵艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一在這1分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被軌道槍射中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在唯一能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是相信亞瑪特拉斯的裝甲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.68,0:20:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦一但進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦的射程範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.55,0:20:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便離開小行星的陰影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在觀測敵艦的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將敵艦擊落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航行管制了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊管制了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好效果音效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現目標\N距離120機何距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.84,0:20:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲發射準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.84,0:20:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等離子液裝填
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粒子加速開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準系統操作正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你手動修正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪需要什麼手動修正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦根本完全沒有迴避啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.22,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接被擊中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.22,0:21:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,損害程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有貫穿裝甲的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電磁性的損傷不算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.73,0:21:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過由於是熱擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中彈的部位裝甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有熔化的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配有耐熱裝甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們這艘戰艦最大的優點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫面切換到損害監視攝影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.94,0:21:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成這艘戰艦會自動引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.71,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是控制耐熱系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經自動啟動散熱系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新型的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然一點也不假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離主砲射程範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.09,0:21:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.12,0:21:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,19
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.15,0:21:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.89,0:21:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,17
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請准許主砲射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.56,0:21:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准許射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離射程範圍內只剩4秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.70,0:21:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.40,0:21:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.31,0:22:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抵達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.41,0:22:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.18,0:22:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是節目播放用的音效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.05,0:22:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.69,0:22:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軌道槍已經停止攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.22,0:22:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.16,0:22:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一發命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.49,0:22:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是亞馬特斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.73,0:22:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用等離子體砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.89,0:22:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮擊沈敵艦的一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.14,0:22:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就第一次戰鬥而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是差強人意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.73,0:22:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欣諾 會議結束了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.53,0:22:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長是基斯卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.36,0:22:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長是泰凱和新特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的操作人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.30,0:23:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.14,0:23:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應節目製作單位的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.54,0:23:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外間宮前總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.64,0:23:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將會來到本艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.34,0:23:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說里歐的伯父啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.48,0:23:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們機個還只是大學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.75,0:23:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.85,0:23:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要打一場漂亮的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.82,0:23:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這艘戰艦擁有\N世界最大的恆星天文台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.39,0:23:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣被擊沈的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.99,0:23:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.47,0:23:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對著夕陽雲朵許願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.84,0:23:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能收到這封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.32,0:23:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能變成一隻小鳥\N現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.69,0:24:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便能飛到你身旁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.50,0:24:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誕生的痛苦 流經的歲月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.84,0:24:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼簾內的風景不斷改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.05,0:24:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們拼命跑 發現闖禍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.35,0:24:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屏住氣 靜靜回到地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.56,0:24:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們拼命往前進 毫不懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.57,0:24:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身遍體鱗傷\N才發現你的溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.19,0:25:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次敬請收看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.63,0:25:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特拉法加的危機